statements.sql: select count(*) as aggregate from `history_orders` as `h` inner join `orders` as `o` on `h`.`id_order` = `o`.`id_order` where `h`.`id_order_status` = 2 and `o`.`date_order` between '2020-07-20' and '2020-07-20'

select count(*) as aggregate from `history_orders` as `h` inner join `orders` as `o` on `h`.`id_order` = `o`.`id_order` where `h`.`id_order_status` = 10 and `o`.`date_order` between '2020-07-20' and '2020-07-20'

select count(*) as aggregate from `history_orders` as `h` inner join `orders` as `o` on `h`.`id_order` = `o`.`id_order` where `h`.`id_order_status` = 3 and `o`.`date_order` between '2020-07-20' and '2020-07-20'

select count(*) as aggregate from `history_orders` as `h` inner join `orders` as `o` on `h`.`id_order` = `o`.`id_order` where `h`.`id_order_status` = 4 and `o`.`date_order` between '2020-07-20' and '2020-07-20'

select count(*) as aggregate from `history_orders` as `h` inner join `orders` as `o` on `h`.`id_order` = `o`.`id_order` where `h`.`id_order_status` = 8 and `h`.`status` = 1 and `o`.`date_order` between '2020-07-20' and '2020-07-20'

select count(*) as aggregate from `history_orders` as `h` inner join `orders` as `o` on `h`.`id_order` = `o`.`id_order` where `h`.`id_order_status` = 9 and `o`.`date_order` between '2020-07-20' and '2020-07-20'
select count(*) as aggregate from `orders` where `priority` = 1 and `date_order` between '2020-07-20' and '2020-07-20'
select count(*) as aggregate from `orders` where `priority` = 10 and `date_order` between '2020-07-20' and '2020-07-20'
select count(*) as aggregate from `orders` where `priority` = 5 and `date_order` between '2020-07-20' and '2020-07-20'

SELECT c.first_name, COUNT(o.id_order) AS cantidad FROM orders o INNER JOIN customer_domicile cd ON o.id_customer_domicile=cd.id_customer_domicile
INNER JOIN customers c ON cd.nid=c.nid where o.date_order>='2020-07-20' and o.date_order<='2020-07-20' GROUP BY c.nid ORDER BY cantidad DESC LIMIT 5

SELECT p.full_name, COUNT(*) AS cantidad FROM providers AS p
INNER JOIN purchase_order_details pod ON p.nit=pod.nit WHERE DATE(pod.created_at)>='2020-07-20' AND DATE(pod.created_at)<='2020-07-20' GROUP BY p.nit ORDER BY cantidad desc
